    <div style="display:flex; flex-direction:column;">

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#1c1917; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          What drives property values in Lota?
          <span style="color:#c4912a; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Lota values are driven by proximity to Lota Creek and the bayside foreshore, the suburb's quiet residential character, access to Manly Boat Harbour and the Cambridge Parade lifestyle precinct, and the school catchments that attract family buyers to this part of the eastern bayside corridor. The suburb sits at a price point below the tighter Manly addresses, which creates consistent demand from buyers who have been comparing the corridor and concluded that Lota delivers the bayside lifestyle they want at a more accessible entry. Properties closest to the water and on well-positioned internal streets attract the strongest competition.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#1c1917; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          How long does it take to sell a home in Lota?
          <span style="color:#c4912a; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Well-priced Lota homes typically sell within 25 to 40 days. Buyers who target this suburb have usually spent time comparing the bayside corridor and arrived at Lota as a considered choice. When the right property appears at a price reflecting recent comparables, those buyers are ready to act. Autumn and spring produce the strongest open home attendance, but genuine lifestyle buyers in this part of Brisbane maintain consistent interest throughout the year.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#1c1917; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          What is the lifestyle like in Lota?
          <span style="color:#c4912a; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Lota offers a quiet, settled bayside lifestyle about seventeen kilometres east of the Brisbane CBD. The suburb is defined by its proximity to Lota Creek, its residential streets, and the outdoor amenity that comes with living close to the water. Manly Boat Harbour and Cambridge Parade in neighbouring Manly are easily accessible for dining, boating, and weekend recreation. It is a suburb where the mix of families and retirees creates a settled, community-oriented character.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#1c1917; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          Is Lota a good suburb to buy in right now?
          <span style="color:#c4912a; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Lota offers genuine value for buyers comparing the Brisbane bayside corridor. The suburb delivers bayside access, quiet streets, water proximity, and Manly's lifestyle amenity at a price point that sits below the most sought-after bayside addresses. Its low stock turnover and consistent demand from lifestyle buyers and families make it a sound long-term owner-occupier consideration for anyone committed to the bayside way of life.</p>
      </details>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

